WEBVTT

00:03:57.834 --> 00:04:00.831
And a year into it,
almost a year to the day,

00:04:00.855 --> 00:04:02.556
I walked into the office,

00:04:02.580 --> 00:04:04.870
and I still remember
setting down my coffee

00:04:04.894 --> 00:04:07.617
and popping out my computer
and there was a phone call

00:04:07.641 --> 00:04:09.886
that said I should go over
to my boss's office.

00:04:10.530 --> 00:04:14.387
You know when your boss
and your boss's boss and HR

00:04:14.411 --> 00:04:15.577
are sitting in the room,

00:04:15.601 --> 00:04:18.272
that it's not going to be good. (Laughs)

00:04:19.212 --> 00:04:22.627
There was no discussion
of why it was happening,

00:04:22.651 --> 00:04:25.283
it was just, "Your job is eliminated.

00:04:25.307 --> 00:04:28.672
You are getting one week's severance pay

00:04:28.696 --> 00:04:30.862
and a one-way ticket back to New Zealand,